{"tid":1520277,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"必也正名：以「反暴政」為這場抗爭的旗號","createTime":"2019-08-30T17:48:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T20:34:04.000Z","uid":82657,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3899f8aadf20c49512d633c7257f7a1c0bf8ee3f","tid":1520277,"uid":82657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T17:48:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%BF%85%E4%B9%9F%E6%AD%A3%E5%90%8D-%E4%BB%A5-%E5%8F%8D%E6%9A%B4%E6%94%BF-%E7%82%BA%E9%80%99%E5%A0%B4%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E7%9A%84%E6%97%97%E8%99%9F/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25BF%2585%25E4%25B9%259F%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%2590%258D-%25E4%25BB%25A5-%25E5%258F%258D%25E6%259A%25B4%25E6%2594%25BF-%25E7%2582%25BA%25E9%2580%2599%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%2597%2597%25E8%2599%259F%2F&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2ZmLjsYRFZgpJr%2B2v3iO%2BBA%3D&h=daa60269\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25BF%2585%25E4%25B9%259F%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%2590%258D-%25E4%25BB%25A5-%25E5%258F%258D%25E6%259A%25B4%25E6%2594%25BF-%25E7%2582%25BA%25E9%2580%2599%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%2597%2597%25E8%2599%259F%2F&h=3f8575db\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%BF%85%E4%B9%9F%E6%AD%A3%E5%90%8D-%E4%BB%A5-%E5%8F%8D%E6%9A%B4%E6%94%BF-%E7%82%BA%E9%80%99%E5%A0%B4%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E7%9A%84%E6%97%97%E8%99%9F/</a><br />\n<br />\n九月罷課前夕，有「聯校反修例罷課聯署」。主題，仍是反修例。<br />\n<br />\n反修例固然是運動的起點，我們至今堅持；但事至如今，一條草案，是否解釋得了如火如荼的時代革命呢？<br />\n<br />\n林鄭本週還在問：「市民最重要的訴求──停止修例，政府兩個多月前已接受了，可抗議還是持續，so what are we going to do？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n她就是要將整場運動講得莫名奇妙，為拗而拗一般。<br />\n<br />\n實情是，連月來群眾攘臂而起，捨己忘身，為的，已不僅是修不修例了，這太淺層；為的，是這個政權，何以硬推乖違民意危害人權的法例，何以縱容甚或指使警黑同體枉法肆暴，何以視市民如草如蟲；為的，是暴政必須革除；為的，是這暴政曾施虐的每一位義士，我們不可捨離不可辜負。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而反暴政，正可為五大訴求提綱挈領：<br />\n<br />\n堅持「撤回草案」，表明香港之事市民作主，教為政者摒棄驕矜。「撤回612暴動定性」，說明當日政府暴力鎮壓才是不當。「成立具公信力的獨立調查委員會」，是要徹查政權暴行。「不追究抗爭者」，是申明人民有權抗暴。「推行普選」，是要避免暴政重臨。<br />\n<br />\n反暴政，是比條例草案的撤回更根本更須全民奮起爭取的總目標。<br />\n<br />\n九月該已不是「反修例罷課」了。<br />\n<br />\n是反暴政罷課。<br />\n<br />\n反暴政遊行。<br />\n<br />\n反暴政人鏈。<br />\n<br />\n反暴政不合作運動。<br />\n<br />\n反暴政抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n必也正名，以「反暴政」（而不是以一個草案的真死假死）為這場抗爭的綱領，道理上支持了抗爭民眾之多，行動上的勇武，以及長流的血汗。政府暴力鎮壓，就得考慮是為這場反暴政抗爭提供理由。政府改弦易轍、實行民主、為暴行贖罪之日，就是反暴政運動終結之時。願有這樣的一天。"},{"pid":"ec5d88b063d975b71fbf6d92992b9b27746f27bf","tid":1520277,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T17:48:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dyrx7H5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDyrx7H5.gif&h=f7c0f28c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2ZmLjsYRFZgpJr%2B2v3iO%2BBA%3D&h=627a119a\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2ZmLjsYRFZgpJr%2B2v3iO%2BBA%3D&h=0b7a4436\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2ZmLjsYRFZgpJr%2B2v3iO%2BBA%3D&h=fc7aa9f3\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"d96f29157434aa482fe92e9bbff6c4800902b0c2","tid":1520277,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T17:48:30.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會 港島見<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.j